-

-
Press and Hold the button on the dolphin tag till you hear a beep

- Find my phone: When the dolphin tag is connected to
your phone, hold the button on the tag and your phone will make a sound.

- Find Dolphin tag: When the dolphin tag is connected to your

beep.

the separated GPS location to make you find the item back more easily.

descriptionHtml:
Dolphin tracker app is an app that helps you to connect Dolphin tag which is a small
Bluetooth device that can be attached to any of items, e.g. your keys, wallet,
luggage, pet, camera and many more. Dolphin tracker is equipped with GPS
tracking feature and helps you to find your lost mobile, lost device, lost
wallet or any other lost item.

With the app on your smartphone you can locate your lost or
misplaced item easily by using its GPS tracking feature. The button on the
device while double clicking also acts as a camera remote which makes taking a
selfie easier.

So whether you forget your thing in a restaurant or theatre or
anywhere in house with the help of a dolphin tag you won’t forget your things.



How Dolphin tracker works:



Step 1: Download app ‘Dolphin tracker’ from App store or Google
Play

Step 2: Turn on Bluetooth. Make sure your phone’s Bluetooth is
on.

Step 3: Sign in with Google account

Step 4: Pair the Dolphin Tag to your phone

-
Hold the dolphin tag close to your phone.

-
Press and Hold the button on the dolphin tag till you hear a beep

And there you are now you can use the tag.



Key features of Dolphin tracker:



- Find my phone: When the dolphin tag is connected to
your phone, hold the button on the tag and your phone will make a sound.

- Find Dolphin tag: When the dolphin tag is connected to your
phone, open the ‘Dolphin tracker’ app and tap the ‘ring’ icon for the tag to
beep.

- Item Lost Alarm: Your phone will sound
alert when it is separated from the beacon device, and the app will also record
the separated GPS location to make you find the item back more easily.

- Separation alarm : Alarm rings on your smart phone & smart tracker as soon as your tracker goes out of range.

- GPS location tracking : GPS location of the tracker is available real time; even when phone is disconnected, last seen location is available.

- Community search : Mark your valuable as lost to activate community search. Every phone running Dolphin tracker app join in, to help you find it.

- Configurable alert range : Set alert range based on your requirement. Alert alarm is triggered based on the set range.

- Long battery life : Replaceable battery; over 6 months of battery life.

- Selfie : Dolphin Tracker comes with shutter button to take photos.

- Wi-Fi Safe Mode: When you connect to those selected Wi-Fi networks, distance alerts are disabled in the Dolphin Tracker app to avoid constant alerts.

- Sleep Mode: You can set the Dolphin Tag device to sleep to save battery life and to avoid unwanted alerts.



Get your Dolphin Tag now: https://bit.ly/32W82Av

descriptionHtml:
Dolphin Tracker App is an innovative and user-friendly mobile application designed to help users keep track of their valuable items, such as keys, wallets, bags, and even wireless earphones. The app connects to a Bluetooth tracker device and provides real-time location tracking, separation alerts, and proximity alerts, ensuring that users can locate their lost items with ease.

The separation alerts feature sends smart notifications to the user's smartphone when their item moves away from the phone, while proximity alerts notify users when their item is within range. These features are particularly useful in crowded places or situations where items can be easily misplaced.

It also has a community search feature that enables users to seek assistance from other Dolphin Tracker users nearby to help locate their lost items.

But that’s not all. Now on the app, you can get free security for your Bluetooth Earphones or TWS Earbuds. Get smart separation alerts on your phone, when your wireless headphones go out of range or are disconnected. Additionally, get notified on your mobile phone when your wireless earbuds come in Bluetooth range or are reconnected. Use these free premium features to easily find, locate & track your TWS earphones.

Now you may listen to your favourite songs on any of your music players without losing your beat, and leave the security concerns of your wireless headphones, earphones & earbuds on us.

This feature is ideal for individuals who use wireless earphones regularly and want to ensure that they do not misplace or lose them.

To connect your Dolphin Bluetooth Tracker or any wireless earphones to the app, simply follow these easy steps:
1. Make sure your BLE tracker or wireless earphone is turned on and within range of your phone.
2. Open the Dolphin Tracker App and select the "Add New Device" option.
3. Follow the on-screen instructions to pair your device with the app.

Dolphin Tracker is a reliable and efficient app that provides peace of mind to users who want to keep track of their belongings. With its smart features and community search option, users can rest assured that their lost items will be found quickly and easily.
